title: Amazon Essentials Skinny Jeans for Women, High Waist, Stretchy Denim
description: SNUG FIT COMFORT: These high-waisted skinny jeans for women are designed to hug your hips, thighs, and legs, providing all-day comfort with a sleek silhouette that complements your natural waist
ALL-DAY STRETCH: Crafted from a cotton blend, these jeans offer great stretch and flexibility, providing a better fit and ease of movement with every wear
WARDROBE VERSATILITY: These high rise skinny jeans for women are great for pairing with cropped tops or any outfit, offering a flattering look to match your unique style
AUTHENTIC DESIGN: Classic five-pocket styling with a reliable zip fly and shank button. Available in three inseam options of Short, Regular and Long
QUALITY YOU CAN TRUST: With consistent sizing, these women's high waisted skinny jeans by Amazon Essentials offer durable craftsmanship for dependable everyday wear

These skinny jeans for women are designed with a snug fit through the hip, thigh, and leg, offering a comfortable high rise that sits beautifully above the natural waist. Crafted from a high stretch denim blend, these jeans provide all-day comfort. The authentic five-pocket styling and zip fly with a shank button closure add to the classic design.
